<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>٨ -<span class="c5"> يحيى بن سعيد القطّان:</span><a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>أخرجه من طريقه أحمد <span class="c2">(٥/ ٥)</span> وأبو داود <span class="c2">(٤٩٩٠)</span> والترمذي <span class="c2">(٢٣١٥)</span> وحسّنه والرّوياني <span class="c2">(ق ١٦٣/ ب)</span>.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
